item.title: By: Lloyd Budd
item.dc:creator: Lloyd Budd
item.description: I've heard of them before. Lots of fun! Personally, I'm not an strings person, and prefer the originals -- or I should say the popular versions. I heard a great segment on the radio recently, about the birth of Rock n' Roll, and how most groups were taking other's styles and songs and making them their own. It sounds like those early cats got this open source thing.
item.content:encoded: I’ve heard of them before. Lots of fun! Personally, I’m not an strings person, and prefer the originals — or I should say the popular versions. I heard a great segment on the radio recently, about the birth of Rock n’ Roll, and how most groups were taking other’s styles and songs and making them their own. It sounds like those early cats got this open source thing.
